In [983]:
sqr=[]
local=[]
city=[]
area=[]
con=[]
lcr=[]
z=[]
y=[]
for i in range(2,5):
    urls='https://www.makaan.com/hyderabad-residential-property/buy-property-in-hyderabad-city?_=1696311984944&page='+str(i)
    page=requests.get(urls)
    soup=BeautifulSoup(page.content,'html.parser')
    print(urls)
    ## x and y
    a=soup.findAll('div',class_='title-line')
    for i in a:
        k=i.strong
        j=k.text

        if j[0].isnumeric():
            z.append(j[0:5])
        else:
            z.append(np.nan)
        y.append(j.split()[-1])
    ## locality
    b=soup.findAll('span',itemprop='addressLocality')
    for i in b:
        local.append(i.text)
    ##city
    c=soup.findAll('span',class_='cityName')
    for i in c:
        city.append(i.text)
    #area
    d=soup.findAll('td',class_='size')
    for i in d:
        k=i.span
        area.append(k.text)
    #construction
    e=soup.findAll('tr',class_='hcol w44')
    for i in e:
        k=i.td
        con.append(k.text)
    ##lakhs
    h=soup.findAll('span',class_='unit')
    for i in h:
        a=i.text
        k=a.replace('L','Lakhs').replace('Cr','Crores')
        lcr.append(k)
    ##Sq.ft

    g=soup.findAll('td',class_='lbl rate')
    for i in g:
        x=re.findall(r'\d+\,\d+',i.text)
        b=x[0].replace(',','')
        sqr.append(b)
    print('z is:',len(z))
    print('y is:',len(y))
    print('sqr is:',len(sqr))
    print('local is:',len(local))
    print('con is:',len(con))
    print('area is:',len(area))
    print('lcr is:',len(lcr))
    print('city is:',len(city))

sqr=[]
local=[]
city=[]
area=[]
con=[]
lcr=[]
z=[]
y=[]
for i in range(2,15):
    urls='https://www.makaan.com/bangalore-residential-property/buy-property-in-bangalore-city?page='+str(i)
    page=requests.get(urls)
    soup=BeautifulSoup(page.content,'html.parser')
    print(urls)
    ## x and y
    a=soup.findAll('div',class_='title-line')
    for i in a:
        k=i.strong
        j=k.text

        if j[0].isnumeric():
            z.append(j[0:5])
        else:
            z.append(np.nan)
        y.append(j.split()[-1])
    ## locality
    b=soup.findAll('span',itemprop='addressLocality')
    for i in b:
        local.append(i.text)
    ##city
    c=soup.findAll('span',class_='cityName')
    for i in c:
        city.append(i.text)
    #area
    d=soup.findAll('td',class_='size')
    for i in d:
        k=i.span
        area.append(k.text)
    #construction
    e=soup.findAll('tr',class_='hcol w44')
    for i in e:
        k=i.td
        con.append(k.text)
    ##lakhs
    h=soup.findAll('span',class_='unit')
    for i in h:
        a=i.text
        k=a.replace('L','Lakhs').replace('Cr','Crores')
        lcr.append(k)
    ##Sq.ft

    g=soup.findAll('td',class_='lbl rate')
    for i in g:
        x=re.findall(r'\d+\,\d+',i.text)
        b=x[0].replace(',','')
        sqr.append(b)
    print('z is:',len(z))
    print('y is:',len(y))
    print('sqr is:',len(sqr))
    print('local is:',len(local))
    print('con is:',len(con))
    print('area is:',len(area))
    print('lcr is:',len(lcr))
    print('city is:',len(city))

sqr=[]
local=[]
city=[]
area=[]
con=[]
lcr=[]
z=[]
y=[]
for i in range(2,15):
    urls='https://www.makaan.com/mumbai-residential-property/buy-property-in-mumbai-city?page='+str(i)+'&_=1696431254022'

    page=requests.get(urls)
    soup=BeautifulSoup(page.content,'html.parser')
    print(urls)
    ## x and y
    a=soup.findAll('div',class_='title-line')
    for i in a:
        k=i.strong
        j=k.text

        if j[0].isnumeric():
            z.append(j[0:5])
        else:
            z.append(np.nan)
        y.append(j.split()[-1])
    ## locality
    b=soup.findAll('span',itemprop='addressLocality')
    for i in b:
        local.append(i.text)
    ##city
    c=soup.findAll('span',class_='cityName')
    for i in c:
        city.append(i.text)
    #area
    d=soup.findAll('td',class_='size')
    for i in d:
        k=i.span
        area.append(k.text)
    #construction
    e=soup.findAll('tr',class_='hcol w44')
    for i in e:
        k=i.td
        con.append(k.text)
    ##lakhs
    h=soup.findAll('span',class_='unit')
    for i in h:
        a=i.text
        k=a.replace('L','Lakhs').replace('Cr','Crores')
        lcr.append(k)
    ##Sq.ft

    g=soup.findAll('td',class_='lbl rate')
    for i in g:
        #x=re.findall(r'\d+\,\d+',i.text)
#         b=x[0].replace(',','')
#         if len(b)!=0:
#             sqr.append(np.nan)
#         else:
#             sqr.append(b[0])
        b=i.text.split(' ')
        a=b[0].replace(',','')
        if len(a)!=0:
            sqr.append(a)
        else:
            sqr.append(np.nan)
        
    print('z is:',len(z))

sqr=[]
local=[]
city=[]
area=[]
con=[]
lcr=[]
z=[]
y=[]
for i in range(2,15):
    urls='https://www.makaan.com/delhi-residential-property/buy-property-in-delhi-city?page='+str(i)

    page=requests.get(urls)
    soup=BeautifulSoup(page.content,'html.parser')
    print(urls)
    ## x and y
    a=soup.findAll('div',class_='title-line')
    for i in a:
        k=i.strong
        j=k.text

        if j[0].isnumeric():
            z.append(j[0:5])
        else:
            z.append(np.nan)
        y.append(j.split()[-1])
    ## locality
    b=soup.findAll('span',itemprop='addressLocality')
    for i in b:
        local.append(i.text)
    ##city
    c=soup.findAll('span',class_='cityName')
    for i in c:
        city.append(i.text)
    #area
    d=soup.findAll('td',class_='size')
    for i in d:
        k=i.span
        area.append(k.text)
    #construction
    e=soup.findAll('tr',class_='hcol w44')
    for i in e:
        k=i.td
        con.append(k.text)
    ##lakhs
    h=soup.findAll('span',class_='unit')
    for i in h:
        a=i.text
        k=a.replace('L','Lakhs').replace('Cr','Crores')
        lcr.append(k)
    ##Sq.ft

    g=soup.findAll('td',class_='lbl rate')
    for i in g:
        x=re.findall(r'\d+\,\d+',i.text)
        b=x[0].replace(',','')
        sqr.append(b)
    print('z is:',len(z))
    print('y is:',len(y))
    print('sqr is:',len(sqr))
    print('local is:',len(local))
    print('con is:',len(con))
    print('area is:',len(area))
    print('lcr is:',len(lcr))
    print('city is:',len(city))

Creating¶

In [2]:
a1=range(1,1000)
b1=['mumbai','kolkata','delhi','bangalore','hyderabad','pune']
urls = []
for i in a1:
    for j in b1:
        url='https://www.makaan.com/'+str(j)+'-residential-property/buy-property-in-'+str(j)+'-city?page='+str(i)
        urls.append(url)

sqr=[]
local=[]
city=[]
area=[]
con=[]
lcr=[]
z=[]
y=[]
for x in urls:
#     urls='https://www.makaan.com/'+str(j)+'-residential-property/buy-property-in-'+str(j)+'-city?page='+str(i)
#     page=requests.get(urls)
#     soup=BeautifulSoup(page.content,'html.parser')
    print(x)
    page=requests.get(x)
    soup=BeautifulSoup(page.content,'html.parser')
    ## x and y
    a=soup.findAll('div',class_='title-line')
    for i in a:
        k=i.strong
        j=k.text

        if j[0].isnumeric():
            z.append(j[0:5])
        else:
            z.append(np.nan)
        y.append(j.split()[-1])
    ## locality
    b=soup.findAll('span',itemprop='addressLocality')
    for i in b:
        local.append(i.text)
    ##city
    c=soup.findAll('span',class_='cityName')
    for i in c:
        city.append(i.text)
    #area
    d=soup.findAll('td',class_='size')
    for i in d:
        k=i.span
        area.append(k.text)
    #construction
    e=soup.findAll('tr',class_='hcol w44')
    for i in e:
        k=i.td
        con.append(k.text)
    ##lakhs
    h=soup.findAll('span',class_='unit')
    for i in h:
        a=i.text
        k=a.replace('L','Lakhs').replace('Cr','Crores')
        lcr.append(k)
    ##Sq.ft

    g=soup.findAll('td',class_='lbl rate')
    for i in g:
        b=i.text.split(' ')
        a=b[0].replace(',','')
        if len(a)!=0:
            sqr.append(a)
        else:
            sqr.append(np.nan)
    print('z is:',len(z))
    print('y is:',len(y))
    print('sqr is:',len(sqr))
    print('local is:',len(local))
    print('con is:',len(con))
    print('area is:',len(area))
    print('lcr is:',len(lcr))
    print('city is:',len(city))

In [963]:
sqr=[]
local=[]
city=[]
area=[]
con=[]
lcr=[]
z=[]
y=[]

a1=range(1,20)
b1=['mumbai','kolkata','delhi','bangalore','hyderabad','pune']
for i in a1:
    for j in b1:
        url='https://www.makaan.com/'+str(j)+'-residential-property/buy-property-in-'+str(j)+'-city?page='+str(i)
    for x in url:
    #     urls='https://www.makaan.com/'+str(j)+'-residential-property/buy-property-in-'+str(j)+'-city?page='+str(i)
    #     page=requests.get(urls)
    #     soup=BeautifulSoup(page.content,'html.parser')
        print(x)
        ## x and y
        a=soup.findAll('div',class_='title-line')
        for i in a:
            k=i.strong
            j=k.text

            if j[0].isnumeric():
                z.append(j[0:5])
            else:
                z.append(np.nan)
            y.append(j.split()[-1])
        ## locality
        b=soup.findAll('span',itemprop='addressLocality')
        for i in b:
            local.append(i.text)
        ##city
        c=soup.findAll('span',class_='cityName')
        for i in c:
            city.append(i.text)
        #area
        d=soup.findAll('td',class_='size')
        for i in d:
            k=i.span
            area.append(k.text)
        #construction
        e=soup.findAll('tr',class_='hcol w44')
        for i in e:
            k=i.td
            con.append(k.text)
        ##lakhs
        h=soup.findAll('span',class_='unit')
        for i in h:
            a=i.text
            k=a.replace('L','Lakhs').replace('Cr','Crores')
            lcr.append(k)
        ##Sq.ft

        g=soup.findAll('td',class_='lbl rate')
        for i in g:
            b=i.text.split(' ')
            a=b[0].replace(',','')
            if len(a)!=0:
                sqr.append(a)
            else:
                sqr.append(np.nan)
        print('z is:',len(z))
        print('y is:',len(y))
        print('sqr is:',len(sqr))
        print('local is:',len(local))
        print('con is:',len(con))
        print('area is:',len(area))
        print('lcr is:',len(lcr))
        print('city is:',len(city))
